# Routes and views

## POST → redirect (PRG)

```js
// ✅ POST handler
return redirect("/envelopes", { type: "success", message: "Saved." });

// ❌ Do not render HTML from POST
return html(body);
```

Catch errors with flash redirects, not 4xx/5xx HTML pages.

## GET flash

Pass `{ clearFlash: clearHeader }` into `html()` on GET responses or flash messages repeat.

## Views

- Full pages: `layout(title, body, { flash, active })`.
- HTMX partials (e.g. `ledgerRowsPartial`) — **no** layout wrapper.
- Escape user text with `escapeHtml`.
- Checkboxes: `value="1"`; absent field = false.

## Tick

Call `schedules.tick(todayISO())` on page loads **except** `/ledger/rows` (infinite scroll must not trigger tick).

## Forms

- Import: `multipart/form-data`, field name `files` (multiple).
- Money form values: `(cents / 100).toFixed(2)`; display via `formatMoney` / `moneySpan`.
- Cadence: `cadenceFields()` + `parseCadenceFields(data)` in views/pages.

Keep SQL and business rules out of `index.js` and views — delegate to services.
